text: Mikhaylovka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Mikhaylovsky Selsoviet, Duvansky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 994 as of 2010. There are 11 streets. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Mesyagutovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Duvansky District
title: Mikhaylovka, Duvansky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
